'''Agelmim aberkan''' (s [[Tifinaɣ]]: '''ⴰⴳⵯⵍⵎⵉⵎ ⴰⴱⵔⴽⴰⵏ''') d yiwen n [[agelmim|ugelmim]] i d-yezgan deg [[Ǧerǧer|yidurar n Ǧerǧer]] gar n ugezdu n [[Tawilayt n Bgayet|Bgayet]] d [[Tawilayt n Tizi Wezzu|Tizi Wezzu]] di [[Tamurt n Leqbayel|Tmurt n Yiqbayliyen]]. 

Agelmim Aberkan yeflal (ɛlay) ɣef weswir n yilel s wazal n 1200 m. Tedla ɣef tjumma yegdan 3 n ihiktaṛen d wazal n 2 m deg telqey.

